  "title": "Software Support / Software Packager [East] - PSCY023",
  "description": "<ul><li>Repackaging the application based on project standards</li><li>Customise the application installation using VB Script and Powershell script</li><li>Troubleshooting application deployment issues.</li><li>Perform software distribution via SCCM & Microsoft In-tune to end point machines</li><li>Troubleshooting issues related Task Sequence, Software and Security Patches deployments</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 3 -5 years of EUCD Support, Application Packaging and ICT End User Computing.</li><li>Good Experience on VB Script and PowerShell scripting for application installation/Uninstallation and Customisation.</li><li>Good Experience on Admin Studio/Install Sheild tool.</li><li>Good Experience on MSI Installer + MST installation</li><li>Good Experience on Microsoft Intune Packaging, Deployment and troubleshooting.</li><li>Candidate with Application troubleshooting skill using logs and Event viewer</li><li>Candidate with SCCM Application troubleshooting experience.</li><li>Possess excellent communication skills to demonstrate and present the solution to the Customer, and the solution will also be made available for future troubleshooting and analysis recorded in proper documentation.</li><li>Demonstrated Basic understanding of SCCM infrastructure (site server roles, DP servers, boundaries)</li><li>Working knowledge in OSD, Software & Security Patch deployments</li><li>Knowledge in troubleshooting issues related to deployments via SCCM</li></ul>",
